abstract: The Texas attorney general has opened an antitrust investigation into how Google ranks search results, striking at the heart of its main search business.
snippet: The Texas attorney general has opened an antitrust investigation into how Google ranks search results, striking at the heart of its main search business.
lead_paragraph: The Texas attorney general has opened an antitrust investigation into how Google ranks search results, the first United States case to strike at the heart of the company’s main search business.

headline.main: Texas Probes Google on Ranking of Search Results
headline.print_headline: Texas Investigates Whether Google Is Distorting Search Results
